    title="How can I take part in this project?"
    subtitle="No matter who you are or what you're interested in, we have a number of ways you can participate in or benefit from TheOpenSource.community."
    tagline="Get involved"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Projects',
        description: "We need community leaders, advocates, and representatives of FOSS projects to help us support you on this site!",
