        title: 'Why sponsor?',
        description:
          "Because you'll help make a HUGE difference, of course! We need the assistance for getting up and running, obtaining software and equipment for our team as well as for others through our programs, funding contributors, and much more.",
      },
      {
        title: 'Can I choose what initiatives to fund?',
        description:
          'Absolutely! If you have an idea already in mind, let us know, else we have a list of specific needs that funding would help us immensely with as well as initiatives that your support could help enable.',
      },
      {
        title: 'What do I get out of it?',
        description:
          "It's totally flexible and up for discussion! We have a few ideas in mind - including different levels of recognition on our website and/or social media - but we're happy to work with you on what would be best for you.",
      },
      {
        title: "Can a custom sponsorship package be assembled?",
        description:
          "Definitely. Just get in touch and let us know what you're thinking, and we'll get back to you with details on our end so we can put together a package that works for all involved.",
      },
      {
        title: 'How can I reach out to sponsor?',
        description:
          "Please reach out to us at sponsors@theopensource.community and we'll get back to you with more details on exactly what's available to fund, different ways you can sponsor us, and how we can best recognize you for your generous contributions.",
      },
      {
        title: 'What if I just want to make a one-time donation?',
        description:
          "We really appreciate you wanting to do so! We plan to support PayPal, Venmo, Apple Cash, and BuyMeACoffee. Please get in touch at contact@theopensource.community if there's something else you had in mind.",
